&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/USA-LAS-VEGAS-TWIST-BY-PIERRE-GAGNAIRE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-4480&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/USA-LAS-VEGAS-TWIST-BY-PIERRE-GAGNAIRE-OFFER-LOGO-MEDIUM.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- LAS VEGAS- TWIST BY PIERRE GAGNAIRE- OFFER- LOGO MEDIUM&quot; width=&quot;114&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Located on the 23&lt;sup&gt;rd&lt;/sup&gt; floor of the elegant Mandarin Oriental Hotel with a stunning view overlooking the Las Vegas Strip, Twist by Pierre Gagnaire specializes in Modern French cuisine by one of the world&rsquo;s most acclaimed chefs. Seasonal &agrave;la carte as well as tasting menus are enjoyed under a canopy of 300 tiny globe lights, creating a lovely glow over the room. Twist is a recipient of the &lt;strong&gt;Forbes Five Star&lt;/strong&gt; award for 2014. Business casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.opentable.com/twist-by-pierre-gagnaire-mandarin-oriental-reservations-las-vegas?rid=36181&amp;amp;restref=36181&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Twist by Pierre Gagnaire website&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or contact Twist by Pierre Gagnaire by phone at +1-702-590-8882 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:molas-fbresv@mohg.com&quot;&gt;molas-fbresv@mohg.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone, local Las Vegas (hotel) phone number and your email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please provide us with a phone number and email so that we can confirm your reservation. For our guests visiting us from abroad, please provide us with an email address so we can confirm your reservation prior to your arrival.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

